episodes.title: The Big Bang
episodes.plot: Broke and low on options, Earn seeks to enter the music industry, by offering to be a manager for his rapper cousin, Paper Boi.

episodes.title: Streets on Lock
episodes.plot: Earn awaits bail after the boys get arrested for their shooting incident.

episodes.title: Go for Broke
episodes.plot: Earn takes Van on a date, still broke. Paper Boi and Darius meet up with a group of thugs for a deal.

episodes.title: The Streisand Effect
episodes.plot: When a blogger begins trashing Paper Boi online, he decides to hunt down the blogger. Darius helps Earn look for a way to make big money fast.

episodes.title: Nobody Beats the Biebs
episodes.plot: Paper Boi attends a celebrity event for the youth and is outwitted by a more famous hip hop artist. Earn faces a case of mistaken identity. Darius runs into trouble at the shooting range.

episodes.title: Value
episodes.plot: When Van meets up with an old friend, things don't go well for her and a sticky situation puts her job on the line.

episodes.title: B.A.N.
episodes.plot: Paper Boi appears on Montague as a guest and must put up with a tedious interview.

episodes.title: The Club
episodes.plot: Earn, Paper Boi, and Darius attend the Primal Night Club. Paper Boi cannot contend with a popular NBA player who is drawing more people toward him. Earn tails an evasive club owner who owes him money.

episodes.title: Juneteenth
episodes.plot: Earn and Van attend a Juneteenth party hosted by a wealthy couple and meet some unusual characters.

episodes.title: The Jacket
episodes.plot: Earn wakes up from a night of partying and goes on a quest to find his navy blue bomber jacket.
